"{\n  \"capCards\": [],\n  \"capHeadings\": [\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"H2\",\n      \"class\": \"heading-medium\",\n      \"text\": \"Let's make\",\n      \"font\": \"\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", Arial, sans-serif\",\n      \"size\": \"105.12px\",\n      \"color\": \"rgb(255, 255, 255)\",\n      \"transform\": \"uppercase\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"H2\",\n      \"class\": \"heading-medium has--align-right has--margin-bottom\",\n      \"text\": \"the moment\",\n      \"font\": \"\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", Arial, sans-serif\",\n      \"size\": \"105.12px\",\n      \"color\": \"rgb(255, 255, 255)\",\n      \"transform\": \"uppercase\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"H2\",\n      \"class\": \"heading-medium\",\n      \"text\": \"blossom\",\n      \"font\": \"\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", Arial, sans-serif\",\n      \"size\": \"105.12px\",\n      \"color\": \"rgb(255, 255, 255)\",\n      \"transform\": \"uppercase\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"H3\",\n      \"class\": \"text-small\",\n      \"text\": \"capabilities\",\n      \"font\": \"\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", Arial, sans-serif\",\n      \"size\": \"10.512px\",\n      \"color\": \"rgb(255, 255, 255)\",\n      \"transform\": \"uppercase\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"reviews\": [\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide is--review w-dyn-item swiper-slide-visible swiper-slide-fully-visib\",\n      \"text\": \"OmarHospitality Brand Manager( 01 )Everything was delivered on time and with zero stress.We needed a clean, elegant setup for a private dinner. The team handled everything quietly and efficiently. The space looked sharp, exactly how we imagined it — no distractions, no noise, just quality.\",\n      \"hasImg\": true,\n      \"imgSrc\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679742110fb07950530154b3/679a5f3906eb048b00164535_review-border.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide is--review w-dyn-item swiper-slide-visible swiper-slide-next\",\n      \"text\": \"LaylaEvent Producer( 02 )They listen — and that shows in the result.We had a layered concept and limited time. They didn’t overcomplicate anything. Just understood the direction, kept it clean, and delivered something that made sense visually and emotionally.\",\n      \"hasImg\": true,\n      \"imgSrc\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679742110fb07950530154b3/679a5f3906eb048b00164535_review-border.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide is--review w-dyn-item\",\n      \"text\": \"ZainFounder, Boutique Fashion Label( 03 )They respected the tone of our brand completely.It’s rare to work with a team that doesn’t try to ‘make it theirs.’ The mood, the materials, the flow — it all felt aligned with what we stand for. Subtle, minimal, but with intention.\",\n      \"hasImg\": true,\n      \"imgSrc\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679742110fb07950530154b3/679a5f3906eb048b00164535_review-border.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide is--review w-dyn-item\",\n      \"text\": \"HanaBride( 04 )It felt like they actually cared about how it would feel.They didn’t push their own taste — they asked the right questions and gave us space to shape it together. In the end, it looked beautiful, but more importantly, it felt like us.\",\n      \"hasImg\": true,\n      \"imgSrc\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679742110fb07950530154b3/679a5f3906eb048b00164535_review-border.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide is--review w-dyn-item\",\n      \"text\": \"TarekCreative Director, PR Agency( 05 )No need for micromanaging — they get it.We briefed once, and they came back with a setup that hit the mark. Visually consistent, functional, and clear. Our clients noticed the difference — it didn’t feel like standard event decor.\",\n      \"hasImg\": true,\n      \"imgSrc\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679742110fb07950530154b3/679a5f3906eb048b00164535_review-border.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"navigation-block prev-slide\",\n      \"text\": \"\",\n      \"hasImg\": false,\n      \"imgSrc\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"navigation-block next-slide\",\n      \"text\": \"\",\n      \"hasImg\": false,\n      \"imgSrc\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"formFields\": [\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"INPUT\",\n      \"type\": \"text\",\n      \"name\": \"name-2\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"Name\",\n      \"class\": \"input-item w-input\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"INPUT\",\n      \"type\": \"tel\",\n      \"name\": \"phone-2\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"Phone\",\n      \"class\": \"input-item w-node-_59910791-ac97-8db7-9d01-9c76afe64922-afe6\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"INPUT\",\n      \"type\": \"email\",\n      \"name\": \"e-mail-2\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"E-mail\",\n      \"class\": \"input-item w-node-_59910791-ac97-8db7-9d01-9c76afe64923-afe6\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"TEXTAREA\",\n      \"type\": \"textarea\",\n      \"name\": \"field-2\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"How can we help you\",\n      \"class\": \"input-item is--large w-node-_59910791-ac97-8db7-9d01-9c76afe\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"INPUT\",\n      \"type\": \"submit\",\n      \"name\": \"\",\n      \"placeholder\": \"\",\n      \"class\": \"submit-button w-button\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tag\": \"DIV\",\n      \"class\": \"button is--submit w-node-_59910791-ac97-8db7-9d01-9c76afe649\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"portfolioItems\": [\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper is--project w-dyn-list\",\n      \"text\": \"Project-82024Project 12024Project 22024Project 32024Project 42024Project 52024Project 62024Project 72024\",\n      \"img\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679a163695df82360ca0d26f/68012d9c8be55ad39e727f91_project5.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"swiper-slide plane-block w-dyn-item\",\n      \"text\": \"Project-82024\",\n      \"img\": \"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/679a163695df82360ca0d26f/68012d9c8be55ad39e727f91_project5.webp\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"class\": \"project-image\",\n      \"text\": \"\",\n      \"img\": null